# Reference section nav (awesome-pages). `...` auto-appends any unlisted page, so
# adding a new reference doc needs no edit here. Titles are pinned only where they
# must differ from the page's H1 (the code-span headings render plainly here).
title: Reference
nav:
  - config-files.md
  - params (+ preprocessing): params.md
  - providers.md
  - stoppedrules.md
  - snat: snat.md
  - conntrack: conntrack.md
  - mangle: mangle.md
  - zones.md
  - interfaces.md
  - policy: policy.md
  - rules: rules.md
  - ...
